                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="space-y-4">
                                <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-red-50 border border-red-200">
                                    <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-red-500 flex items-center justify-center text-white flex-shrink-0">
                                        <i class="fas fa-question"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <p class="font-semibold text-gray-800">File not loading?</p>
                                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">
                                            Ensure it's a valid CSV format with <span class="font-mono bg-gray-200 px-1">comma</span> delimiters. Check that the file isn't corrupted and has proper line endings.
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                
                                <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-orange-50 border border-orange-200">
                                    <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-orange-500 flex items-center justify-center text-white flex-shrink-0">
