                                        <p class="font-semibold text-gray-800">NaN values in results?</p>
                                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">
                                            Check for non-numeric values in the KPI column. Remove any text, symbols, or empty cells that might be causing the conversion error.
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                
